	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "Created `analysis/companies/google.md` following the same structure and detail level as the Apple and Microsoft summaries. Key highlights in the file:\n\n- **Key Metrics table**: $110.0B revenue (+14% YoY), $2.27 EPS, both beats\n- **Segment Performance**: Search ($61.5B, +13.9%), YouTube ($12.0B, +14.3%), Cloud ($14.9B, +30.7% with 14.1% operating margin), Other Bets ($0.5B revenue / -$1.1B loss)\n- **AI & Search Monetization**: AI Overviews at ~3B daily queries approaching monetization parity, ~$2.5B annualized Cloud AI run-rate, TAC ratio improving to 19.4% (from 21.3%)\n- **Guidance**: $75B 2026 CapEx plan, Q1 2026 revenue $112–115B, Cloud at 26–30%\n- **Market Reaction**: GOOGL +4.6% on earnings day to $221.34, new all-time high; consensus PT raised 15% to ~$248\n- **Sector Implications**: Positive digital ad read-through for Meta/Snap; Cloud competitive positioning vs. AWS (19% growth) and Azure (35% CC)" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/confidence> "0.8"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/agent_id> "723a325b-7e1c-4f4b-a3cb-3e6dfec2fa3f" ;
