	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/memory_type> "semantic" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/created_at> "2026-03-25T00:46:40.502494+00:00" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/content> "`analysis/README.md` has been created. Here's what the document covers:\n\n**Structure:**\n- **Executive Summary** — 4 paragraphs opening with the single most significant takeaway (AI revenue is real, accelerating, and margin-accretive across all four companies), then covering the CapEx supercycle, cloud war dynamics, and sector-by-sector validation\n- **Key Findings** — 10 bulleted headline findings with supporting data, spanning AI revenue metrics, CapEx commitments, cloud growth rates, advertising strength, and Apple's Services momentum\n- **Company Performance at a Glance** — summary table with revenue, YoY growth, EPS beat/miss, and stock reaction for all four companies; includes a fiscal calendar note to prevent confusion on reporting periods\n- **Sector Impact Summary** — 2–3 key takeaways each for Semiconductors, Cloud Computing, and Ad Tech\n- **Top Correlations** — 5 notable cross-company patterns: AI margin accretion, services outperformance, Apple as semiconductor read-through, conservative guidance pattern, and the platform-vs-intermediary bifurcation\n- **Methodology** — concise note on public data sourcing\n- **Report Index** — links to all eight underlying documents" ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/confidence> "0.8"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#double> ;
	<http://tesserai.io/ontology/agent_id> "402f5a7c-ef71-4c03-b3ef-2c4c6e7d36c1" ;
