# === memory-8bee2191-8f48-412f-95bf-8fd89a5938d1 ===
<urn:tesserai:twin:memory-8bee2191-8f48-412f-95bf-8fd89a5938d1> <http://tesserai.io/ontology/createdAt> "2026-03-25T00:21:09.208682Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> ;
